    <item>
      <title>卡塔尔航空：电子商务繁荣将推动货运量增长 10%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/e-commerce-boom-to-drive-10-freight-growth-qatar-airways-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[卡塔尔航空货运部门表示，购物者对快速送货的强烈需求将推动今年航空货运量增长 10%，抵消主要经济体经济可能放缓带来的阻力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/e-commerce-boom-to-drive-10-freight-growth-qatar-airways-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 04:09:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>SpaceX 碎片落入飞机航线后，航班被迫改道</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/flights-diverted-after-spacex-debris-falls-into-path-of-planes</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，SpaceX星际飞船试飞失败并发生爆炸，捷蓝航空公司和美国航空集团公司运营的商业航班被迫采取避险措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/flights-diverted-after-spacex-debris-falls-into-path-of-planes</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 01:24:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>索尼取消了另外两个 PlayStation 项目，全面撤退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/sony-cancels-two-more-playstation-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该公司告知其子公司 Bend 和 Bluepoint，它将与这两家公司合作，确定下一步行动，并尽量减少裁员]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/sony-cancels-two-more-playstation-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 23:09:02 GMT</pubDate>
